{"tid":1557751,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"燒山係一條打破不割席既計謀","createTime":"2019-09-10T08:50:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T08:51:29.000Z","uid":167938,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"372c065a83b01cf95e79911decdbefea3fdc4e03","tid":1557751,"uid":167938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T08:50:28.000Z","msg":"有人講過 <br />\n要燒點解唔燒啲有用既建築物 例如政府部門<br />\n<br />\n假設成功燒山 社會點樣睇燒山<br />\n到底割唔割席好<br />\n所以<br />\n燒山只有地產商係既得利益者<br />\n<br />\n我代表抗爭者講<br />\n抗爭者並<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不會</span></span>想燒山<br />\n<br />\n抗爭者只會想燒狗屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3271c04b280a9584bd6cd00a9de817f464eb7763","tid":1557751,"uid":167938,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T08:51:29.000Z","msg":"所以親中人士如想屈我地<br />\n請燒[black]<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">狗</span></span>[/black]"}]}